"         SokalScore = e",
"         <sup>",
"          (0.0116*(Age-43.4)+0.0345*(SpleenBelowCoastalMargin-7.51)+0.188*(sq(Platelets/700)-0.563)+0.0887*(BlastPercent-2.1))",
"         </sup>",
"        </span>",
"       </td>",
"      </tr>",
"     </table>",
"     <br/>",
"     &nbsp;",
"     <br/>",
